'''Wessiri''' could refer to:
*'''[[Ethen Wessiri]]''', [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] citizen on [[Voss]] during the [[Galactic War]]
*'''[[Diric Wessiri]]''', husband of Iella Wessiri and [[Lusankya (prison)|''Lusankya'']] [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoner]] [[Brainwashing|brainwashed]] into one of [[Ysanne Isard]]'s [[Sleeper agent/Legends|sleeper agent]]s
*'''[[Iella Wessiri Antilles]]''', [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]] [[Police officer/Legends|officer]] and Rebel [[Spy/Legends|spy]] who became a member of [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]] and wife of [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]
